      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... a pretty heavy way to look at it. You're saying that since nothing matters, the most logical thing is to just give up? Like, if there's no point to the struggle, isn't it actually more \"rational\" to just exit rather than keep fighting a losing battle against a void that doesn't care?",
